caption:
@parkroyalbeachroad celebrates World Tapas Day on 18 June 2020 with a brand new tapas menu in a collaboration between Executive Chef Vincent Aw (Ginger) and Executive Chef Zeng Feng (Si Chuan Dou Hua Restaurant). The Gourmet Asian Tapas Flight (serves 2-3 pax at $29.80) features Crispy Rack of Lamb with Thai Mint Sauce, Wagyu Beef Cheek Satay with Hazelnut Sauce, Large Prawns with Minced Chilli, as well as Deep-fried Scallops with Minced Prawn Paste Sauce.
.

Pair the sensational tapas flight with their brand new cocktail, Stay Gin-spired. Enjoy a complimentary Stay Gin-spired Cocktail * (U.P. S$12.80) for the first 20 online orders of the limited edition Gourmet Asian Tapas Flight. Valid for orders placed on 18 June 2020 only. You can place your order online via www.panpacific.com.shop-parkroyalbeachroad. Enter promo code FREEGIN upon checkout to add the complimentary cocktail to cart.
